        "text": "The Des Moines Area Food Bank operates at multiple locations to provide food assistance to the community. \n\nOne location is at the Des Moines Marina Farmers Market, located at 22307 Dock Ave S, Des Moines, WA 98198. Additionally, they offer Grab'n'Go meals for kids and teens at 8 sites, which can be picked up by parents and do not need to be eaten on-site. You can find more details on their website at www.myfoodbank.org/meals-for-kids.html.\n\nAnother location is at Midway Park, located at S 221st St & 29th Ave S, Des Moines, WA 98198. For more information, you can contact the food bank at (206)-878-2660. More information can be found on their website at www.myfoodbank.org/meals-for-kids.html.\n\nThe Des Moines United Methodist Church is another location where the food bank operates. Families can visit once a month and receive a mix of canned, fresh, and frozen food.
